 set forth in these guidelines these guidelines are subject to modification from time to time as the board of directors deems appropriate in the best interests of the company or as required by applicable laws and regulations document view code of business conduct and ethics    mb audit committee charter   kb compensation committee charter   kb nominating and corporate governance committee charter   kb corporate governance guidelines    mb  add file to briefcase investor relations overview press releases events  presentations corporate governance management board of directors committee composition anonymous reporting financial information sec filings proxy materials – vote here annual reports quarterly results key ratios stock information investment calculator analyst coverage investor faqs contact us shareholder tools shareholder briefcase printed materials email alerts download library snapshot rss news feeds search print this page email this page share this page share this on delicious digg facebook linkedin twitter what is this share this on  delicious digg facebook linkedin twitter social media lgi homes inc  press releases the right builderfor youbuilding homes with great value and great prices in excellent locations throughout texas arizona new mexico colorado georgia north carolina florida and washington takes something special dedicated to ourcustomersthank you for choosing lgi homes now that youre a home owner we want you to know that we are just as committed to you today as we were when you were a home buyer your first timehomebuyers guideweve taken an interest in firsttime homebuyers and have made it a priority to provide them with high quality homes and affordable financing options and a nostress home purchase process press releases year all years         all releases lgi homes introduces new floor plans at meriwether community jul    kb   woodland wash july   globe newswire  lgi homes inc nasdaqlgih introduces new floor plans at the meriwether community